{"tid":2371742,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"Ben Affleck Ana de Armas 分手","createTime":"2021-01-19T05:55:18.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-19T10:02:03.000Z","uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"eb46bcdb74ba20f615781b3aa245704a3fdd2275","tid":2371742,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-19T05:55:18.000Z","msg":"48歲的「小班」班艾佛列克（Ben Affleck）去年3月戀上32歲的「龐德女郎」古巴女星安娜德哈瑪斯（Ana de Armas），上月還傳出2人在洛杉磯同居，看似十分甜蜜，美國《時人》雜誌周一卻報導，他倆現階段人生目標不同，安娜決定掰了小班，10個月的戀情嘎然中止。<br />\n<br />\n他們去年初在紐澳良拍攝驚悚片《深水》（Deep Water，暫譯）墜入情網，3月傳出緋聞，安娜4月隨即在IG分享2人合照，大方認愛。小倆口2020年出雙入對黏TT，安娜上月還傳出準備出售位於洛杉磯威尼斯的住宅，搬到小班的洛杉磯豪宅同居，沒想到卻在2人交往將近1年後選擇和平分手。<br />\n<br />\n《時人》報導，他倆透過電話協議分手，「他們討論過無數次，關於彼此的未來，共同決定要分開」。安娜過去幾星期都待在家鄉古巴，她17日現身好友的YouTube頻道，剪掉一頭長髮，換成了可愛的鮑伯頭，看起來更加甜美。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/resizer/rwDDURCF_xWC6OqHWz_9Bxemijs=/535x329/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/EJQJOUM3SJFM3NQBKZEVDAPZXA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FrwDDURCF_xWC6OqHWz_9Bxemijs%3D%2F535x329%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FEJQJOUM3SJFM3NQBKZEVDAPZXA.jpg&h=f8b365fa&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"187db50902a3915e319a7d4b3d292ef2dc63b6c9","tid":2371742,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-19T05:55:50.000Z","msg":"消息人士告訴《時人》雜誌：「小班現在沒和安娜交往了，是她提出分手的。他們的關係很複雜，安娜不想定居在洛杉磯，但小班必須留在洛杉磯，因為他的孩子都住在那裡。」小班與前妻珍妮佛嘉納預有3名子女──14歲的紫羅蘭、11歲的莎拉費娜和8歲的山繆。<br />\n<br />\n熟識他倆的友人則補充說明：「這（分手）是他們共同的決定，過程和平。」、「他們處於不同的人生階段，深愛也尊重彼此。小班希望持續專注在自己的生活和事業上，接下來有3個工作等著他，他也是一家之主。他們都很滿足於自己現在的生活。」<br />\n<br />\n《紐約郵報》則報導，安娜想生小孩，她現在30出頭，正是生育的關鍵年齡；不過，小班和前妻珍妮佛嘉納已有3名子女，他拒絕承諾生更多小孩，2人在這一點上面沒有共識。消息人士透露：「小班現在不想成立一個新家庭，他原本的家庭一直、也持續是他的重心。」另外也有友人表示，「他們彼此之間仍有愛，2人也有可能會復合，大家相信分手可能只是短暫的」。"},{"pid":"454591cf6368c894195065db7100adf11cc03333","tid":2371742,"uid":162539,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-19T05:56:23.000Z","msg":"肥Ben幾型"},{"pid":"4c4a723d41763b3f0de004a7bc34b6dc2079b5d5","tid":2371742,"uid":36509,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-19T05:56:31.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://twitter.com/ArmasUpdates/status/1351350565704519685\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FArmasUpdates%2Fstatus%2F1351350565704519685&d=aWm579aYkHvvwdD7ZyOwrLnp9gp%2BSvHPFRLSSJzTNPo%3D&h=e86ac565\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FArmasUpdates%2Fstatus%2F1351350565704519685&h=879ad137\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/ArmasUpdates/status/1351350565704519685</a>"},{"pid":"14ad5f03fb2219fa96e1bfed2444d27bf3534de5","tid":2371742,"uid":41343,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-19T05:57:49.000Z","msg":"垃圾工人已經把Ben家門口的Ana紙牌掉了<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ysUmnVr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FysUmnVr.jpg&h=09328466&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JmgcuAu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJmgcuAu.jpg&h=272a9040&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xf8N2Vy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fxf8N2Vy.jpg&h=6ad48e79&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"723b97da33a3d9dc644197ddc3f048f4e56832e1","tid":2371742,"uid":93986,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"14ad5f03fb2219fa96e1bfed2444d27bf3534de5","tid":2371742,"uid":41343,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-19T05:57:49.000Z","msg":"垃圾工人已經把Ben家門口的Ana紙牌掉了<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ysUmnVr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FysUmnVr.jpg&h=09328466&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JmgcuAu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJmgcuAu.jpg